name: Flume
description:
Concert or art installation? @ KL 2019

The lasers weren't even the most interesting visual during this show. There was onstage tai-chi, printer demolition, spray painting, metal carving. 

I adore Flume because he's a bizarre dude who makes bizarre music and performs them in the most bizarre shows.
